posting_body: ['420 West Fullerton Parkway', 'Unit #204', '1 bedroom 1 bath', '$1,318 rent', 'Lease Assumption Aug 1, 2022 - January 31, 2023 (6 months).', 'This is not a sublease, you will have your own lease.', 'Location:', '- just east of Clark and Fullerton', '- Short walk to the lake and beach', '- Bus stops at corner', '- Right next to the park', '- Food and two gyms just around corner.', 'Trader Joe’s, Marianos, Target and Walgreens nearby', '- Lively downtown scene.', 'Colectivo, Gaslight Bar and Grill etc.', 'Website: <URL>', 'Rent/sq feet:', '- $1,318 rent and 600+ sq feet.', 'Cost of a 350sq foot studio in building is now $1,409.', 'Great deal for spacious 1 bedroom near lakefront', 'Parking: lots of street parking available or if spot is needed there is building parking on east and west side of the building', 'A/C has already been paid for through 2022.', 'Brand new A/C unit.', '****', 'If interested, please apply directly through', '<URL> and contact Sr Property Manager Ashanti Cole to indicate interest in unit 204 at Beachwalk Apartments.', 'Phone is 833 297 6939', '****please also reply to me through Craigslist so I can let Ashanti know of your interest']
